  "uploadNotes": "Linseed cultivation taken by authors from Nguyen (2012), original data from France. Linseed processing from Bacenetti (2017), selected by us as a proxy. Authors have used daSilva for soybean cultivation data and dalgaard for soybean processing. Given these data are just proxies, we decided to omit them and just specify that the soybean meal is from Brazil.",
